Interface IRevisionBucket

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IBucket
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RevisionRootBucket

    public interface IRevisionBucket
extends IBucket
    One bucket representing unique buckets within one revision. Normally this should not occur since buckets can be represented by multiple versions in the buckets tree.
    Author:
    Sebastian Graf, University of Konstanz
